CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, March 9, 1946, pg. 19, reads: "Fifteenth Anniversary - Mr. and Mrs. John Adams celebrated their fifteenth wedding anniversary at the home of Mrs. Catherine Walker of Humber Way, last Saturday evening.  The occasion also marked Mrs. Walker's birthday.  Corp. Henry Jones, home on furlough, was among the guests. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Women, including Catherine Walker, and men, including Corp. Henry Jones, surrounding John Adams and Mrs. Adams for their anniversary party in Walker Home, Humber Way, Hill District
